Usage ./source_code.sh [FILE_TYPE] [DIRECTORY]
		WHERE 
         FILE_TYPE is a type of source code file like a java, c, cpp, go, php, js, html
         DIRECTORY is a path to dircetory with yours sources
         
Results of collection can be found in source_code.txt file in directory when you call this script

Notes: this script works only in *nix-like enviroment. NOT IN WINDOWS
